    +getName(): String
    +getSchema(): ArchetypeSchema
  }

  note top of EventArchetype
    Defines the structure and semantics of an event that can be emitted or
    received by a system via its effectors and receptors.

    **Consistency Rules**
    - "name" MUST be maximum 80 characters long.
    - "name" MUST be unique among all entities classified as "archetype".
    - "name" MUST match the name of the schema.
    - If its schema is deleted, the event archetype MUST be deleted.
  end note

  SystemicPrimitive <|-- EventArchetype : is
  EventArchetype "0..*" o--> "1" ArchetypeSchema : has
  
